title: Greg Harbour, professional skater
itunes:title: Greg Harbour, professional skater
description:
I am pumped to bring you this interview with professional skater, Greg Harbour. We chat about his introduction to both independent music and skating at the same time, why falling is cathartic and relating to your parents.
